Amtech Systems hires financial consultant . Amtech Systems Inc , a maker of equipment used in the production of semiconductors , on Wednesday said it has BC Capital Corp as its merger and acquisition consultant . " Management is committed to completing one or more acquisitions to further the company ' s growth strategy , " J . S . Whang , president and chief executive officer , said in a statement . Miami - based BC Capital Corp will provide advice on acquisitions , mergers and joint ventures . 
